data.description: Secluded home conveniently located just off the freeway and a couple miles from town. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home is nestled back off the road with a private setting on just over 3 acres. The home features an open floor plan, full walkout basement plumbed for a 3rd bathroom, a deck off the dining area that overlooks the yard, trails along the property leading to the large pond at the back of the property.  There is also a garden area that is fenced in with an outbuilding that has water.
